&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of MiFID requirements and regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to work independently and prioritize tasks effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong communication and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Detail-oriented with a high level of accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Certification in Compliance or related fields is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
