&lt;p&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;IT Compliance Manager&lt;/strong&gt;, you will conduct in-depth evaluations of our technological infrastructure to ensure compliance with financial market regulations and data protection standards. This role entails a strong understanding of regulatory environments, meticulous attention to detail, and the capability to sustain high-performance levels in a quantitative trading context.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a dedicated professional who demonstrates high autonomy and accountability, someone who reliably completes tasks, proactively identifies and addresses compliance issues, and swiftly integrates into the dynamic rhythm of our organization.&lt;/p&gt;
