&lt;p&gt;Eqvilent is a Dubai-based proprietary quantitative and algorithmic trading firm operating across multiple jurisdictions: UAE, UK, Malta, India, Hong Kong and many others. Our legal function sits at the heart of the business: advising on regulatory compliance, supporting commercial expansion, and partnering directly with business leaders to drive smooth execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Legal Secretary provides comprehensive administrative and document support across all workstreams of the Eqvilent legal function. The role is hands-on, detail-intensive, and requires a candidate who takes pride in precision, maintains complete discretion, and operates proactively rather than waiting to be directed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Legal Secretary at Eqvilent is not a passive filing role. The successful candidate will be expected to own defined processes end-to-end, including the preparation of standard-form documents without supervision, the maintenance of live legal databases, and the coordination of multi-party signature and execution workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
