&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are seeking &lt;strong&gt;Software Developers&lt;/strong&gt;, preferably with commercial experience in low and ultra-low latency projects to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will possess intelligence, calmness, thoughtfulness, and an unruffled demeanor, with a strong focus on detail and a passion for streamlining business procedures.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
