&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with the trading desk to ensure smooth and efficient trading operations while adhering to risk management protocols&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
